snippet.title: メリルくるりんち (Meril Kururinchi) Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Fun Umihara Kawase inspired wire action game created in 2007 by Sasakoge Kobo
Download available here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/186JFCJ76FC2XgX1B8VOCiM2PDFYMhX6y/view?usp=share_link
I couldn't find any gameplay footage outside of an incomplete playthrough uploaded to Niconico so I figured I'd upload a full one to YouTube.
Naturally, this playthrough is spliced as performing a no-death run would be very difficult to pull off.
